Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}‫תרגום לעברית — That One Gerbil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:09.99,Warning,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\fscx0\fscy0\clip(0,0,0,0)\org(0,0)}Your media player does not support the subtitle format used in this episode.\NSubtitles will likely not function properly.\NPlease use one of the recommended video players, preferably mpv:\Nhttps://mpv.io
